Package user_management

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observable
    Interface which contains the notifyObservers method used for the Observer pattern.
    PeopleToNotify
    Interface which contains the update method used for the Observer pattern.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Courier
    Implementation of Courier, extends the PhysicalUser class.
    CourierFactory
    CourierFactory class enables creating a new courier thanks to a factory pattern.
    Customer
    Implementation of Customer, extends the PhysicalUser class.
    CustomerFactory
    CustomerFactory class enables creating a new customer thanks to a factory pattern.
    Main_application  
    Manager
    Manager is a physical user of the system, it extends PhysicalUser.
    ManagerFactory
    ManagerFactory class enables creating a new manager thanks to a factory pattern.
    PhysicalUser
    A physical user has a name, surname, birthdaydate, username, password, phone number, email and an adress.
    Restaurant
    Implementation of Restaurant, extends the lUser class.
    RestaurantFactory
    RestaurantFactory class enables creating a new restaurant thanks to a factory pattern.
    User
    A user has an ID, a name, a username, a password, a phone, an email, an adress.
    UserFactory
    Abstract UserFactory, part of the Factory-Pattern to create users.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FidelityCardDoesNotExistException
    Exception which appears when the user enter the name of a fidelity card which does not exist.
    KindOfContactDoesNotExistException
    Exception which appears when the user enter a kind of contact which does not exist.
    RestaurantNotFoundException
    Exception which appears when the name of the restaurant does not exist in MyFoodora system.
    SameUserNameException
    Exception which appears when a user is trying to choose a username which already exists.
    UserNotFoundException
    Exception which appears when the name of the user does not exist in MyFoodora system.
    WrongUserNameOrPassWordException
    Exception which appears when the user cannot connect with this password and username.
